{"tid":2515111,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【包傻包到糉】入冊前有幾多包幾多","createTime":"2021-05-03T17:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T17:29:35.000Z","uid":187232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6be80b0aec1380744fb53978366e55bf297554b1","tid":2515111,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<br />\n<br />\n好老實咁同大家講，好快就判刑<br />\n包埋今年呢一次糭，幾年都唔會再見到大家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時只有一間小小黃店同一間online shop有得賣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COXd3hwAeuT/?igshid=5vvdejktsdh2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOXd3hwAeuT%2F%3Figshid%3D5vvdejktsdh2&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=15837bed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOXd3hwAeuT%2F%3Figshid%3D5vvdejktsdh2&h=eabd9a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/COXd3hwAeuT/?igshid=5vvdejktsdh2</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/shirleyswine_?igshid=1btzsooz8bwp9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fshirleyswine_%3Figshid%3D1btzsooz8bwp9&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=300f2a80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/shirleyswine_?igshid=1btzsooz8bwp9</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/880290942818017/permalink/904985433681901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F880290942818017%2Fpermalink%2F904985433681901%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=7c5a9e48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/880290942818017/permalink/904985433681901/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZJyXHMtLZEQWUx19FeLBu2YZzw3uws1osLAjHRdrHPkK?filename=19dUy9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19dUy9N.jpg&h=75efd8c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n非常十分感激沙田瀝源街市小店嘅老闆娘，一直以嚟都低調力撐我地，今次為咗我哋入冊前呢個心願， 親自教我地包糭，鼓起勇氣開名同借地方比我地寄賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmefBxoJWp3Kd6Kc8KRAiz7uuMVmYfkRNBrE3o3MSVc6ie?filename=CqGyPJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqGyPJb.jpg&h=aef659ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n碗仔翅、魚蛋、燒賣、雞蛋仔....<br />\n明明係咁普通平凡嘅嘢，點解會咁好味嘅? <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地喺入面嘅時候, 大家可唔可以答應我地多啲幫襯老闆娘?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaxsWSMUMzPo11dAnC9bUH8Bxv7oYKqazuZFwRBhvboAy?filename=taoELgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtaoELgH.jpg&h=ce3d1f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地真係好想入冊前，可以比各位手足買到食到自己親手包嘅糭<br />\n真係好好味架，食完人都聰明咗，考試100分<br />\n我叫你試吓呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3DsutsgMCsnaEi2S1E1odvXoGzGPcj6rDpZcSinFeER?filename=KcjHH3N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcjHH3N.jpg&h=e02ed90b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a20e18c67675050b5e91c82eddfae9b51ea3f02a","tid":2515111,"uid":285851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500ccdaf7f48f81ed3c49be3f8c0adea1be49c62","tid":2515111,"uid":343450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"推呀🥲"},{"pid":"5ef553e51b15c9c18275bb98439f10aa3691c67d","tid":2515111,"uid":317616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"9698ed30f7a4d83bee860bc306e554955a9c72d7","tid":2515111,"uid":317616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"f29e72c34d15f6517ace4c5d3d8dac3c7abe63c3","tid":2515111,"uid":275102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97f737e461a21a7fd89b4c7cadaaa5d068a78410","tid":2515111,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"真係包傻包到糉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmegsVNu99JqZv9uPD85fYPknyaWKLJ9xuwpdqciYCim3i?filename=EPAPobf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPAPobf.jpg&h=0eab636d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2751593be0becdf6bceb90a482c0d87b95e1eb9e","tid":2515111,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:27:15.000Z","msg":"推 你哋會唔會係個到坐場？"},{"pid":"1ca35bfbbfb602b7fbf31be0b788ccbf4c125981","tid":2515111,"uid":321048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ccf5c1fcc7a72aa5cb2a5ca2d715d4ca616486","tid":2515111,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:29:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22bd2bddaee878f7bf0017e51bf921979230e3c5","tid":2515111,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97f737e461a21a7fd89b4c7cadaaa5d068a78410","tid":2515111,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"真係包傻包到糉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPAPobf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPAPobf.jpg&h=0eab636d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好錯focus<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPdHWpkoBwL1rngc4wHPa48hc5wtJKA2TBqBEA4o9FR1D?filename=5aGfiL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna